      "id": "start",
      "type": "narrative",
      "chapter": "第一章 · 初入仙门",
      "text": "你站在青云宗的山门前，云雾缭绕间隐约可见亭台楼阁。一位白须老者缓缓走来，目光如炬地打量着你。\n\n\"年轻人，你可知修仙之路艰辛万分？前方无路可退，唯有一往无前。\"他说道。\n\n你深吸一口气，感受到体内微弱的灵气在流转。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "恭敬行礼，请求拜入宗门",
          "weight": "branch",
          "weightHint": "这将决定你在宗门中的地位起点",
          "changes": {
            "reputation": 5,
            "mind": 3,
            "show": true,
            "feedback": { "style": "toast", "duration": 2500 }
          },
          "next": "gate_test"
        },
        {
          "text": "展示自己修炼所得，证明资质",
          "weight": "critical",
          "weightHint": "高风险高回报的选择，可能影响后续剧情走向",
          "condition": { "var": "cultivation", "op": ">=", "value": 10 },
          "conditionDisplay": "disabled",
          "changes": {
            "cultivation": 3,
            "spiritual": -10,
            "show": true,
            "feedback": { "style": "toast" }
          },
          "next": "gate_test"
        },
        {
          "text": "询问关于修仙界的疑问",
          "weight": "minor",
          "changes": {
            "mind": 5,
            "show": true
          },
          "next": "gate_test"
        },
        {
          "text": "默默观察四周环境",
          "weight": "cosmetic",
          "changes": {},
          "next": "gate_test"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "gate_test",
      "type": "narrative",
      "chapter": "第一章 · 入门考验",
      "text": "老者微微点头，示意你跟随他进入山门。穿过层层云雾，你们来到一处广场。广场中央矗立着一块巨大的测灵石，散发着淡淡的蓝光。\n\n\"将手放在测灵石上，让我看看你的资质。\"",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "全力运转灵力，冲击测灵石",
          "weight": "critical",
          "condition": {
            "all": [
              { "var": "spiritual", "op": ">=", "value": 20 },
              { "var": "mind", "op": ">=", "value": 20 }
            ]
          },
          "conditionDisplay": "hide",
          "changes": {
            "cultivation": 10,
            "spiritual": -20,
            "hp": -5,
            "show": true,
            "feedback": { "style": "inline" }
          },
          "next": "inner_gate"
        },
        {
          "text": "平稳输出灵力，保持稳定",
          "weight": "branch",
          "changes": {
            "cultivation": 5,
            "spiritual": -10,
            "mind": 2,
            "show": true
          },
          "next": "inner_gate"
        },
        {
          "text": "先调整心态，再缓缓输入",
          "weight": "minor",
          "condition": { "var": "mind", "op": ">=", "value": 25 },
          "conditionDisplay": "disabled",
          "changes": {
            "mind": 5,
            "cultivation": 3,
